<div class="container">
    <div class="row welcome">
        <h2>Welcome to Betting App!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        {{!--  --}}
        <div class="col left-bar">
            <h2>How to Play</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Betting App, the app that lets you make casual bets with your friends!</p>
            <p>To use Betting App, sign up for a free account by clicking on the Login button. Once you have an account, you can go to your Profile page to propose a bet to a friend. If they accept, the bet is on!</p>
            <p>Once you have decided the bet, you and your friend both vote on who won the bet. If you both agree, the winner of the bet is recorded, otherwise it counts as a tie.</p>
            <h2>Stats</h2>
            <h3>Total Bets to Date</h3>
            <p>So far, {{stats.num_bets}} bets have been made with Betting App. Will you make the next one?</p>
            <h3>Biggest Win</h3>
            <p>The biggest win to date is ${{stats.big_win}}. Nice!</p>
            <h3>Biggest Loss</h3>
            <p>The biggest loss to date is ${{stats.big_loss}}. Bummer!</p>
        </div>
        {{!-- Sidebar --}}
        <div class="col right-bar">
            <h2>Recent Bets</h2>
            <ul class="list-group">
                {{#each bets as |bet|}}
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <h3>{{bet.winner.username}} won ${{bet.amount}}</h3>
                    {{#each bet.users as |user|}}
                    <p>{{user.username}} bet ${{user.stake.amount}}</p>
                    {{/each}}
                </li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
